It was all smiles and laughter on the 14th of February when OPPO Nigeria decided extend this year’s Love Season experience to its service center in Ikeja, Lagos. Every customer who visited OPPO Service center was greeted to a surprise valentine’s day gift, this was OPPO’s way of showing love to its loyal customers who use their smartphones and IoT devices.  Following the commencement of this year’s Valentine Campaign themed “Say It with A Gift” OPPO took it even further to express its gratitude and love to its loyal customers online and offline with lots of gift and shopping vouchers. Customers who visited the service center had a welcoming experience of awesome Valentine’s Day gifts, photo experience and many more exciting activities. The Valentine themed photo booth afforded customers the opportunity to create beautiful love themed memories with their friends, colleagues and loved ones who came into the store with them. This love gesture by OPPO was not only targeted at customers, but members of staff as well as they received gift bags from the brand in appreciation of their dedication and commitment. It was an intentional event that created an atmosphere of relaxation and a sense of belonging to all OPPO Nigerian customers who happened to walk in on Valentine’s Day.  To get more exciting update on OPPO activities, new products and discount offers follow them on all social media platforms
